This module is very simple to translate !
(Thank you to Joke Evers !)
You have only to translate the two files : 
* remarks.fr or remarks.en into a new file "remarks.###"
* help.html

After that, you have to modify in the file var.init
the variables :
* taal ('fr' for french or 'en' for english or '###' for your language)
* appletlanguage

